'''單詞每分鐘'''（{{lang-en|'''Words per minute'''}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]'''wpm'''），是量度[[打字|打字]]與[[速讀|速讀]]的速度的[[计量单位|單位]]。對於一個單詞的定義，每5個[[字符|字符]]視為一個[[單詞|單詞]]。<ref>Ahmed Sabbir Arif, Wolfgang Stuerzlinger [http://www.cse.yorku.ca/~wolfgang/papers/textperfmetrics.pdf Analysis of Text Entry Performance Metrics] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cse.yorku.ca/~wolfgang/papers/textperfmetrics.pdf |date=20110813085336 }} Dept. of Computer Science & Engineering York University</ref>例如，"I run"會當成一個字， "rhinoceros" 會當成兩個字。"Let's talk"亦會當成兩個字，因為[[空格键|空白]]視為一個字符。

==字符輸入==
一個專業的打字員應有50至70wpm，部份更會要求80至95wpm（通常是調對工種）。<ref name=Ayres&Martinás2005>{{citation |year=2005 |author=Ayres, Robert U |authorlink=Robert Ayres (scientist) |author2=Martinás, Katalin |chapter=120 wpm for very skilled typist |page=41 |chapterurl=http://books.google.com/books?id=ksxK7J95IF8C&pg=PA41&dq=typists+%22120+words+per+minute%22&hl=en&ei=9sbqTL_zF4HvcMeu1YgL&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CEoQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=typists%20%22120%20words%20per%20minute%22&f=false |title=On the Reappraisal of Microeconomics: Economic Growth and Change in a Material World |place=Cheltenham, UK & Northampton, Massachusetts |publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing |isbn=1-84542-272-4 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ksxK7J95IF8C&printsec=frontcover&dq=reappraisal+microeconomics&hl=en&ei=ZNnqTKykO8XQcaqq1ckK&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |accessdate=22 November 2010 |archive-date=2014-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140113225004/http://books.google.com/books?id=ksxK7J95IF8C&printsec=frontcover&dq=reappraisal+microeconomics&hl=en&ei=ZNnqTKykO8XQcaqq1ckK&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>

另一個較少用的量度單位為'''CPM'''。它是指每分鐘輸入的字符，通常在一些打字程式中使用，以準確地量度一段時間內的打字速度。'''CPM'''除以5便可轉成'''wpm'''。在20世紀，打印機通常使用'''CPM'''，現代的打印機則使用'''PPM'''（pages per minute，頁每分鐘）。

目前，最快的打字記錄為216wpm。在1946年芝加哥，Stella Pajunas-Garnand使用IBM電腦在一分鐘內完成。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bigsiteofamazingfacts.com/history-of-typewriters |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |archive-date=2013-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130515165828/http://www.bigsiteofamazingfacts.com/history-of-typewriters |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.owled.com/typing.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |archive-date=2018-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826043812/http://www.owled.com/typing.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www-03.ibm.com/ibm/history/exhibits/modelb/modelb_4509PH04.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |archive-date=2016-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720232526/http://www-03.ibm.com/ibm/history/exhibits/modelb/modelb_4509PH04.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deskstore.com/INFORMATION-1/en/Plan-Your-Office/Believe-it-or-not |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-08 |archive-date=2020-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807234602/https://www.deskstore.com/INFORMATION-1/en/Plan-Your-Office/Believe-it-or-not/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==數字輸入==
數字輸入用來測量輸入員在數字鍵的輸入速度。一般來說，需要經常輸入數字的工作，例如從事銀行或股票相關工作，會使用這個量度方法。它的單位是'''按鍵每小時'''（Keystrokes per hour），簡稱'''KPH'''。大部份工作會要求有8,000至10,000KPH。<ref>For KPH required for data entry jobs, please see various job websites such as Monster.com</ref>

==手寫==
若一個人把已記好的文字寫出，平均有31wpm，若抄寫資料，則有平均22wpm。<ref name="multiple">Brown, C. M. (1988). Human-computer interface design guidelines. Norwood, NJ: Ablex Publishing.</ref>

使用[[速记|速记]]的話，手寫速度可大幅提升。在速记比賽，最佳成績為282wpm。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gregg.angelfishy.net/anaboutg.shtml|title=About Gregg Shorthand|accessdate=2011-07-08|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020005456/https://gregg.angelfishy.net/anaboutg.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==閱讀==
wpm亦是量度[[閱讀|閱讀]]速度的單位，常用於[[速讀|速讀]]比賽。

[[美國|美國]]成人可閱讀250至300wpm。[[校對|校對]]時，文字顯示在屏幕有180wpm的校對速度，印在紙張有200wpm。<ref>Ziefle, M. (1998), Effects of display resolution on visual performance, Human Factors, 40(4), 555–568.</ref>

